title: VA Indie Easy Rock DEC 2013 - In The Dark (Dutch Treat I2)
description:
Its the "Zwarte Piet" edition and fills our hearts full of anxious expectations. Moving around, long before slavery was invented. Dancing around in his native African suit (with feather) and less offensive than Father Christmas, reducing Christmas (the day we celebrate the birth of Jesus), to money and consumption. In Holland we are angry about the stupid comments by an (important?) VN lady (with obviously still some issues) about our National children's party. Sinterklaas is simply first (and quite another person than our imaginary Grandfather) and stays. Together with our friends... Enjoying some Indie in the meantime.
